Catching up on this - we have an active initiative underway for it (as we've heard this request from several customers) https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-1821. @Rakesh's team is working on the ability for a customer to access the post-processed split document through the results API. This is targeted for Q3.

@Kaustubh (KD) I'll close out your ticket as it's a dupe of the one above (but thank you for creating it!).
